image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>一个家庭</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>哪怕穷的家徒四壁</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>只要有一个善良、节俭、乐观和整洁的女人在料理,这样的家庭仍是心灵的圣堂与快乐力量的源泉。母亲为了社会贡献的最主要的产品就是你的孩子,除了自发的爱以外,母亲必须学习教育的艺术,否则,任何教育改革都将是徒然。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>母亲的形象至始至终都会影响每一个人的人生,也许很多人不会认真地思考和承认这个问题,但是这确实是一个不能否认的真理!一个人从小到大,只要他(她)的母亲伴随着他们的成长里程,母亲的一切,包括母亲的形象;母亲的做人原则;母亲的思想......<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>都会在不知不觉中始终影响他们的孩子,那些孩子就是生活中的你我他。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>一.坚强的母亲教会孩子在困难面前不会怯懦</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>在人们的一些思维里都是把女人当作柔弱的代表,似乎只有男人才能配得上&ldquo;坚强&rdquo;二字。其实在现实生活中,真正地遇到困难,能够不惧艰难困苦,一直坚持下去的往往就是那些看起来比较软弱的女人,她们甚至在有些方面比男人显的还要坚强的执著。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>像王桂荃(梁启超的二夫人)女士,在梁启超离世之后,带着九个孩子度过了令人无法想象的岁月,即使在文革的动乱年代也没有动摇她的坚强信念,在她去世以后,梁思成和兄弟姐妹一起在父亲墓旁种下一棵&ldquo;母亲树&rdquo;,以此纪念这位伟大的坚强母亲。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>二.心胸宽阔的母亲让孩子学会展望未来</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>女人的胸怀历来被文人描写的及其狭窄,甚至还有民间的俗语:女人头发长见识短。好像世界上只有男人的胸膛是宽阔的大道;而女人的心胸只是山间的羊肠小路。然而有很多的女人的胸怀让我们敬佩,真是这些女人的胸怀让我们懂得一个母亲的宽阔胸膛会对孩子起多大作用。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>佐藤富子&mdash;&mdash;(郭沫若在日本的同居女人)这个现代人也许并不知道她的名字的女人,在被郭沫若无情抛弃之后,一个人居然抚养着五个未成年的孩子,直到十五年以后见到郭沫若。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>三.善良的母亲让孩子懂得悲天悯人</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>人类社会最可怕的就是行为的残酷和精神的冷漠,可是我们谁也不能否认很多人好像无法躲避这两种悲惨的现实。虽然有时候这两种状况是一种&ldquo;不可抗力&rdquo;造成的,但是大多数情况下是人为的现象铸就的,那就是一些人从小就没有一个善良的母亲,从此他们的人格受到严重的扭曲。&ldquo;悲天悯人&rdquo;的情怀虽然有后天的修养与教育形成,但是它仍然是来源于孩子母亲的善良根基。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>比尔盖茨就曾说过,自己在母亲那里得到的是&ldquo;虔诚和善良&rdquo;,我们在比尔盖茨对全世界贫困地区的大量捐款上就可以看到母亲的印记。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>四.冷静镇定的母亲使孩子学会坚韧不拔</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>在很多文学作品中,或者是有形宣传影像中,我们大多是情况下看到的是遇到灾难时候的母亲,不是嚎啕大哭就是绝望的想到自杀,然而在现实生活中,我们见到的在如今人们难以形容的场面上,一个母亲的镇定和冷静足以让人终生不能忘记。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>当年中国的第一夫人王光美先生(此称呼是对任何值得尊敬的人可以使用)被造反派在万人大会上批斗侮辱,她那叫人敬佩的表情,不但激励着她自己的孩子坚韧不拔地度过了十年的非人岁月,也为我们树立了一个光辉的母亲典范。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>五.有修养的母亲会铸就孩子的品质</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&ldquo;修养&rdquo;这个名词在每个人身上的体现,那就是一个人的品质,一个人的品质优秀似乎又能成就他的事业。那么修养即使在成年之后如何&ldquo;建设&rdquo;,其实大多数的修养还是从母亲那里点点滴滴&ldquo;浇灌&rdquo;的。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>母亲尊老爱幼,孩子自然就会上行下效;母亲节俭有度,孩子自然就会拒绝奢华;母亲彬彬有礼,孩子自然就会谦虚不傲......<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>著名指挥家汤沐海的母亲蓝为洁女士就特别重视孩子的修养,汤沐海成为世界级的指挥家,绝不单单是他的艺术造诣所决定的,西方人很欣赏汤沐海的高雅修养和高尚品质,他们认为这些肯定来源于蓝为洁女士对孩子的影响。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>六.文化资深的母亲会影响孩子的深刻思考</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>有文化的母亲绝对会影响孩子的思维,如果是文化资深的母亲似乎就更能影响孩子的深刻思考,就像一个还不会走路的孩子在大人手牵手的带领下慢慢学会走路一样。有文化的母亲从孩子出生那天起就在每一天的生活里,一点点地影响孩子,让他们杜绝粗俗;让他们远离简单;让他们知道深刻......<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>著名作家金庸就曾经说过,他对小说的人物内心深处的探索很多受母亲的文化影响。金庸的母亲徐禄是徐志摩的姑妈,在那个时候就读过高中,并能写一手漂亮的水笔字。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>每一个人的母亲都在以他们各自的形象影响着自己的孩子,虽然在这里举出的都是名人的母亲,这不等于我们没有注重平凡的母亲,只是这里所举出的母亲形象大家都知道和熟悉,所以他们就具有一定的代表性。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>其实即使是我们自己的母亲,他们身上同样会有这些美好的人格特征和精神品质,唯一的区别就是只有我们自己清楚。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>女人应具有的品质</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>1、情趣</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>情趣需要一些天分,但是后天的修炼也比不可少。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>要会讲一些笑话,要能带动气氛,大家都期望你能唱歌的时候能够唱得很好,玩得时候要能玩得开心,别人不快乐得时候,能够带动他快乐。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>情趣,需要一些知识,需要一些幽默,需要一点小资,还需要一些发自内心得快乐。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>情趣,可以很高尚,也可以有些低俗,但是不可以没有。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>一个有情趣得女人,往往是一个快乐得女人,至少也是一个能够创造快乐得女人,这样女人,别人乐而往之,怎能不留恋?</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>2、平和</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>这个社会变化太多,我们不要让自己的心也荒来荒去,懂得保持内心平和的女人,就象闹市中的一间静谧的茶馆,让人忍不住想歇足休息。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>平和的女人,要求不是那么多,不会动不动就嫉妒别人的富贵和幸运。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>虽然同样感慨社会多变、人生无常,平和的女人却懂得守住内心的一点淡泊。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>平和的女人,要求不是那么多,不会给自己很多压力,当然,也不会给男人很多压力,所以,平和的女人,总是让男人很轻松,能够成为男人心灵休憩的港口。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>平和的女人,没有那么执着,不会歇斯底里,也不会哭天抢地。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>如果,她看到自己心爱的男人,和别的女人在一起,不会抢上前去大闹一通,而是,静静地,坚决地、慢慢远离那个男人。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>平和的女人,懂的保护自己。不会让自己那么容易受到外界的干扰。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>所以,平和的女人,总能让男人感觉到安宁、放松,让男人在伤心的时候、疲倦的时候甚至太过激动的时候,都想要和她在一起。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>平和的女人最懂得温柔。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>3、坦然</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>知道自己那里好看,那里不好看,知道自己有什么优点有什么缺点,觉得这些很正常,就是一种坦然。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>知道男人有那些好,那些不好,也觉得这很正常,不苛求完美,就是坦然。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>明白一个衣冠楚楚的男人,也会有委琐的时候,并不觉得这很可耻,泰然处之,也是坦然。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>坦然的女人不卑不亢,不会谄媚、也不会自卑。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>坦然的女人,深刻理解事实无常,明白生活的变化往往不是由自己能控制的,所以悲伤的时候不会刻意隐藏,快乐的时候懂得充分享受。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>这样的女人,活的很清醒,也很真实。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>坦然的女人,努力但却不异想天开,懂得承受。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>不压抑,不做作,自然舒服,让男人觉得很真切,让男人觉得&ldquo;原来生活就是这个样子,也没有什么不好&rdquo;。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>4、善良</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良不是看到路边的乞丐给他2<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>块钱,也不是一次又一次的忍受男人的背叛而总是原谅他,善良不是付出、不是软弱更不是退让,而是当你可以伤害别人的时候、而不伤害别人的一种品质。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>当你和他分手的时候,善良是你不会辱骂他、报复他、决不放手,而是,挥挥衣袖,转身离开。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>当朋友家庭出现闹剧的时候,善良就是你在幸乐祸的同时,懂得伸出双手提供帮助。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良就是你从不主动伤害别人,不会纠缠不休,懂得适可而止。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良就是不会利用男人的弱点来攻击他,虽然你知道他都又什么弱点。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良就是你们分手后,财产一人一半,而不是把他驱逐出门,一分不给。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良的女人,才会在分手后,仍然告诉孩子那个男人是他的爸爸,而不是仇人。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良的女人,才懂得为自己留一条后路,不把事情做绝。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>善良的女人,才不会让男人担心害怕,男人对她才会念念不忘。在这样的女人面前,男人才不会又戒心,才能够觉得安全。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>5、精致</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>精致的女人就象一件高档的珠宝,熠熠生辉、细腻璀璨,让男人爱不释手。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>精致,不一定就需要高档的衣服、首饰或其他道具来塑造,更多的是一种生活态度。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>切一壶茉莉花茶的时候,放2<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>颗玫瑰、加一勺蜂蜜,是一种精致。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>品茶的时候,知道用自己心爱的瓷杯、或者透明的玻璃杯装上,而不是用一次性纸杯,是一种精致。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>抄好的青菜,用细白瓷光洁的盘子装上,摆出秩序的样子,是一种精致。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>每晚睡觉前,仔细地在镜前端详自己,并且高兴地想&ldquo;我还是美丽的&rdquo;,也是一种精致。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>知道施华洛世奇的水晶和地摊上的水晶,有何区别,并不一定去买,是一种精致。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>知道在宴会上该穿礼服、工作时该穿套装、睡觉时该穿性感睡衣,是一种精致。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>精致的女人,注重品质、细腻,让男人觉得高尚。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>精致的女人,美好、珍贵,让男人感觉到来之不易,必须好好珍惜。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>精致的女人,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>才懂得享受生活</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>才能够承受富贵</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>才不会当男人富贵的时候想要放弃她。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>6、聪慧</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>聪慧,和女人的学历并无绝对关系,而是一种理性,一种思维方式。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>聪慧得女人,不以卖弄自己得学历和知识为荣,而是更加注重运用。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>聪慧得女人,懂得辨别男人,知道什么是好、什么不好,不会把心血浪费在不适合得男人身上(聪慧如黄蓉,就知道把郭靖打造成一代大侠,而不是逼着他只过小日子)。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>聪慧得女人,知道什么样得朋友值得交,什么样得人不可接触。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>聪慧,是一种洞悉世事得感悟,清醒、塌实,同时,乐在其中。</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>7、自然</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>自然的女人就是,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>不会为了让人觉得矜持而故做矜持状;不会为了给别人淑女的感觉而东施效颦。</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 14px; word-break: normal&quot;>8、真诚</span></p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(70,70,70); word-break: normal; border-top: 0px; list-style-image: none; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>对帮助你的人,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>真诚的道谢</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>而且要看着他的眼睛</span>,<span style=&quot;line-height: 21px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal&quot;>让他能感受到你的真诚</span>;</p><p style=&quot;border-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px simsun; word-wrap: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: norma