);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>1.床对女人最重要的意味是奉献和牺牲,似乎没有女人会觉得上床的意义是自我索取,女人总是会说,我献出了我的身体,看看,多么悲壮!</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>2.上床对女人意味着情感关系的确认,女人虽然也很挣扎,但一旦上了床就会想:我已经是他的人了,这是一种正常的思维方式,男人可不会这么认为。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>3.上床对女人意味着身体的归宿感,身体和心灵的双重归宿感对女人来说就是爱情。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>4.上床对女人意味着增加了索爱的砝码,所以女人更容易在不确定关系时几匆匆的上床,这也正是容易失策的地方。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>5.上床对女人意味着开始有操守心,如果不上床,女人还可能左顾右盼,但上了床就不一样了,她开始讲究从一而终。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>6.上床对女人意味着开始关心男人的衣食住行,只要上了床,女人就开始觉得与这个男人已经是一个整体,对他的关心甚至与强过自己。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>7.上床对女人意味着做女人的开始,男人在床上的成长是了解了女人,而女人在床上的成长是激发了潜能,激发了母性。</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 2em