15442646	十二生肖节气运势:小寒(0105~0119)	<p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>小寒,是二十四节气中的第二十三个节气。这几天大家盼着北京下雪,实际上在20号节气转换成大寒以前,下点雪对夏天的气候也是比较好的,<span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;>俗语言:「小寒大寒不下雪,小暑大暑田开裂」,也就是这两个节气,如果够冷,接下来的气候就是有利於农耕的好天气。</span></span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>而搭配着二十四节气的推进,十二生肖的运势又有什麽需要注意的呢?就让艾菲尔老师独家帮你分析。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><img src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/01/09/138925173688787704.jpg&quot; /></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【鼠】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>脱口而出的玩笑话或许会刺伤他人,请尽量避免取笑或说他人坏话。不管是工作或者金钱,甚至是你的感情,这几天要有好消息,都要靠你的人际网络介绍。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【牛】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>你最近容易受到小人的诱骗,请坚持自己的步调,不要听信道听途说。想要避免厄运,请记得行善礼佛。跟关系不错的好友出门,会比你想像的收获更多。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【虎】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>最近财务的问题会困扰你,物品请以实用为主,不要追求不实际的时髦流行。工作有隐藏性的异动,最近正是你参加实用补习课程的好时机,百利而无一害。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【兔】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>想突破目前的困境,请化被动为主动,否则事情只会越来越多。对於无聊或无法达到的要求,要学会拒绝。和情人的争吵,点到即可,你要关心更多的,是自己的健康问题。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【龙】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>多主动与身边的人沟通,你曾以为万分严重的事,也许是误会了。学会释怀,对你的身心灵健康非常重要。不要总是一头热的追求某个目标,耐心和悠闲才是长久之道。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【蛇】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>有个人紧盯着你的一举一动,这个人可能是你的长辈或上司,虽然心里不舒服,但是请维持礼貌,否则後患无穷。请坚定你的心,给情人关怀。小心应酬过多的花费。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【马】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>只要坚忍不拔,就可以克服困难。即使闷闷不乐,也要万事小心,最近可能会有血光和破财。爱情感到孤独寂寞,无法时刻相守,但是每日的问候可以令感情增温。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【羊】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>努力地做好本分工作,不满和挑剔的话,说出口只是让事情变得更棘手。不要有借贷的关系,否则要小心有去无回。外出走走会有好运,但是别因此花费太多的金钱喔!</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【猴】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>在感觉万事顺利的时候,请不要过度放松。把能做的都先做好,才能更好地应付突如其来的事件。分隔两地的情人,可以拿起照片,细细回味美好时光,补充爱的能量。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【鸡】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>人际交友在这段日子显得特别重要,不妨好好整理家居环境,也许会有重要的贵客上门。与别人意见不同时,保持沈默也许是你唯一能做的抵抗,但只有勇敢沟通才能使状况转好。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【狗】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>你最近的贵人运不错,即使遭遇挫折,也无需太过沮丧。只要抱持着乐观坚定的信念,万事都能水到渠成。承诺的是要努力做到,受人帮助请适当回馈。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; min-height: 19px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9);&quot;>【猪】</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times;&quot;><span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px;&quot;>你也许开始对自己的平淡生活感到失望,该是时候充实自己丶主导命运了!所有的钱都要花在刀口上,别再散漫度日了。然而多方尝试前应该要多评估,否则惊喜恐怕会变成惊吓。</span></p><div>&nbsp;</div><div><img src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/01/09/138925182582101605.jpg&quot; /></div>
