max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=480667a88695138052b&quot; /></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>孔令辉的影响力很难用具象的数字来描绘,他的球迷多为女性,散布在祖国大江南北,甚至是世界各地。因为他,一批球迷将&ldquo;成为体育记者,甚至是乒乓球专项记者&rdquo;作为自己的职业规划。</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/06/1391692019992.jpg&quot; /></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>2006年10月12日,孔令辉正式宣布退役,并在无锡宣读4000余字的退役感言。</p><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</div><p style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;567&quot; height=&quot;720&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=480de57c99095a921ec&quot; /></p></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>孔令辉退役后,诸多媒体以&ldquo;乒坛从此无王子&rdquo;为标题进行报道,赞誉他为&ldquo;不可复制的乒坛偶像&rdquo;</p><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;561&quot; height=&quot;420&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/06/1391692021736.jpg&quot; /></div><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;>2013年,对于孔令辉是特殊的一年,事业上他正式担任国乒女队主教练。</div><p style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;614&quot; height=&quot;412&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=48019d8addbd16949af&quot; /></p></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>但是情感上,与<span class=&quot;wp_keywordlink_affiliate&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><a title=&quot;查看马苏中的全部文章&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-decoration: none; outline-style: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.yangfenzi.com/tag/%e9%a9%ac%e8%8b%8f&quot;>马苏</a></span>11年恋情以分手告终,此后又闹出&ldquo;嫩模车震门&rdquo;,可谓是风波不断。为何孔令辉的感情路如此坎坷,我们且从命理学上试着分析。</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/06/1391692024807.jpg&quot; /></p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>孔令辉与第一任女友马苏的相识相恋,曾被看做文体恋的经典代表。<br />2002年釜山亚运会后,孔令辉与马苏在一次朋友聚会上相识,老乡见老乡一见钟情,自此开始了长达11年的爱情长跑。</p><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=480a1709d51ef5b814d&quot; /></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>从星座学上来看,孔令辉是天秤座。天秤座男生举止言行十分注意分寸,对周围发生的一切都兴致勃勃,不仅知道事情的来龙去脉,而且还知道什么时机对成功最有利。<br />北京奥运前,孔令辉携马苏大方做客《鲁豫有约》,讲述甜蜜恋爱史。</p><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;556&quot; height=&quot;407&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=48072f7cafe4979960e&quot; /></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>天秤座男生最善于发现哪些人与他志趣相投。天秤座男生的优势是:富有魅力、温文尔雅、性格平稳、目光敏锐,具有合作精神。天秤座男生品格正直,和蔼可亲,闪耀着魅力的光辉;天秤座男生温柔、娴雅,他需要欢欢乐乐地生活,需要忠贞不渝的友谊和爱情。</p><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;<img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/06/1391692029595.jpg&quot; /></div><div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;>孔令辉探班马苏,两人幽会被记者拍到</div><p style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 620px;&quot; src=&quot;http://pic4.zhongsou.com/img?id=480622542c5e0d6c08f&quot; /></p></div><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;>但就在与马苏交往的11年过程中,两人分分合合闹剧不断,都曾有<span class=&quot;wp_keywordlink_affiliate&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><a title=&quot;查看劈腿中的全部文章&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-decoration: none; outline-style: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.yangfenzi.com/tag/%e5%8a%88%e8%85%bf&quot;>劈腿</a></span>传闻冒出,孔令辉还曾二度被拍到与《红楼梦中人》的<span class=&quot;wp_keywordlink_affiliate&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px;&quot;><a title=&quot;查看杨舒婷中的全部文章&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-decoration: none; outline-style: none;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.yangfenzi.com/tag/%e6%9d%a8%e8%88%92%e5%a9%b7&quot;>杨舒婷</a></span>亲密牵手逛公园</p><p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-indent: 24px;&quot;><img alt=&quot;&qu