13699441	羊毛衫情结(图)	&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;插画:田威&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;顾惟颖<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一到冬天,上海格外阴冷,家家户户从箱柜里翻出羊毛衫,拎出来一抖开,一股樟脑丸的特殊气味散开,很温和的怪味道,倒不让人讨厌,反而说明衣服被爱护得很细心。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上海人爱好绒线类的织物,尤其爱羊毛衫。在过去,一件高级好看的毛衣,会代表着一个人的家境与层次。西装外套可能是人们应对重要场合的行头,而毛衣是日常装备,好坏更显见。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上海女子,有爱编织毛衣的传统,上海话里叫“结绒线”。我有一个三十出头的女友,自己还未成家,一年四季以给周边亲友家小孩结小衣服为乐,每完成一件就发照片在微信朋友圈展示,好几种针法变换着织,花样不少,说是中学时外婆教的。在过去,家中女眷里总会有人擅长织毛衣。一团又一团各色毛绒线,满满一袋子,一双玉手架起两根尖长的毛线针,一针一线编织出彩色的温暖来,正面看过去,钢针撑出的那尚未完成的织物,仿佛是一只迷你的凤凰,翅翼张开,尾羽长长地拖着。喜欢织毛衣的女孩子,哪怕尚未嫁娶,也早早就拥有了一点母性,至少善于关心人,那毛衣,毕竟是替人御寒的。喜好织毛衣的女人,也应该是生性比较安稳的,坐在冬天的煤油炉子边一天接一天织出一件衣服,直到完成的那一刻,都是淑静的。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我姨妈就是个爱与钢针为伴的女人,她身体不好,不到四十就请长期病假在家休息,于是一年四季就看见她总是在结绒线,除了姨父、表哥的衣物以外,她也给家里其他人织,什么毛衣、毛裤、围巾、手套……她都能织。我爸从中百公司买了件羊毛背心,姨妈拿去看了看,样子就统统记得了,不久以后,家里所有男性,无论大人小孩,都有了一件“山寨”版羊毛背心。姨妈织毛衣的时候对自己要求很高,经常见她手里一件“作品”的领子和两个袖子都结好了,忽然不晓得她哪里不满意,统统拆了重头来过。有时候,姨妈一边让家里其他女人举开双手,供她绕毛线,一边绕一边聊家常。假如没有人帮她,她也有好办法。古代的纺织娘有织布机,城市里的女人织毛衣,也有她们摆开的阵势,比较常见的就是将一张红木方凳倒置,四条木腿绕上毛线。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;织毛衣的姨妈,心里仿佛只有那绒线团与长针,发起脾气来,那些道具也牢牢地捏在手里。表哥小时候在学校捣蛋被老师上门告状,姨妈体罚他,竟然不拿尺来打,而是将他拉下裤子按在沙发上,用毛线针扎他屁股,其实估计也就是吓唬吓唬他,不见得真的扎下去,但是那种威慑估计对小家伙很管用,表哥的屁股在长针下拼命挣扎,他一边哭一边喊“以后不敢了呀—”。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因为从小到大一直穿妈妈织的毛衣的表哥,再捣蛋,也是奶油的。在过去,穿羊毛衫的男子,绝对是有品的。那种全羊毛的高领毛衣,绒面丰满,亮光下有光泽,女孩子的脑袋靠过去,十分柔软,带着一股羊毛特有的香气。靠更近一点,皮肤上被静电微微刺到,有一瞬间的微疼,那是距离太近“来电了”。上世纪80年代的奶油小生不见得穿西装,但是会在冬天穿羊毛衫,再系一条宽大的羊毛围巾,那就是各大高校白马王子的标准打扮。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;以前有一种说法,假如有个女人肯给男人织一件毛衣,那么这个女人才算是被男人搞定,所谓,她的心已经被征服。这种衡量“搞定”的标准,其实颇浪漫,不像今天的男人哪怕给一个女人买100件衣服,也不见得彼此搞定对方。有时候蛮怀念那个穿蝙蝠袖羊毛衫的年代,那时候上海年轻人的偶像是沈小岑、张瑜,男男女女用四喇叭播放着Modern&nbsp;Talking的迪士高音乐扭动胯部,人人都会唱《明天会更好》。<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这两年蝙蝠袖毛衣似乎又流行起来,但是人们不见得因此怀旧,却害怕明天。
10519395	爱情公寓4剧情透露.	  <br/>  在第24集大结局中,诺澜为什么要说“对不起”?因为在之前的网球友谊赛中,诺澜的摔倒是一记假摔!<br/>  在第22集游戏夜中,诺澜向一菲坦白,自己对小贤有意思。 <br/>  从一菲的一系列反应中,诺澜确认了一菲是自己的潜在情敌。所以上演了第24集中的那次摔倒。<br/>  诺澜的这记假摔成功的赢得了曾老师的同情,并借机用实际行动(一个吻)主动向曾小贤表白。 <br/>  这就是关于“对不起”的全部真相吗?不,事情远没有这么简单!最后,当曾小贤在3602和3601之间徘徊的时候,3601内的一菲为什么一直对着着手机发呆?<br/>  没错!真相只有一个:诺澜将下面这张照片用曾小贤的手机发给了一菲!(详见第20集)<br/>  一菲看着从曾小贤手机发来的这张照片,正好印证她之前的那个梦:“你会祝福我们的对吗?”<br/>  最后的“未完待续”的结局应该是这样:一菲选择了放手,选择了祝福诺澜和小贤。因此,诺澜的这句“对不起”有两个含义。一、对不起曾小贤,赢得他同情的是一记假摔。二、对不起一菲,自己故意造成了一菲和曾小贤之间的误会。补充:个人认为诺澜和小贤不会长久,他们会在爱情公寓4的第十集左右分手,原因是小贤对一菲旧情难忘,而诺澜选择了主动退出。而一菲和小贤最终将会在爱4的大结局的时候在一起。(如果编剧为人厚道的话)虽然若男挺美的我还是支持菲贤
15874066	揭秘日本宅女深闺令人脸红心跳不止	  <br/>  揭秘日本宅女深闺令人脸红心跳不止(组图) <br/>  <br/>  揭秘日本宅女深闺令人脸红心跳不止(组图) <br/>  <br/>  揭秘日本宅女深闺令人脸红心跳不止(组图) <br/>  <br/>  揭秘日本宅女深闺令人脸红心跳不止(组图) <br/>    最近,日本摄影师川本诗织推出了写真集《Daraku部屋》(堕落部屋),展示了许多日本宅女的房间和她们“宅宅更健康”的生活状态。<br/>    照片中,“daraku部屋”内堆满了垃圾和杂物的颓废样子让很多日本人诧异不已。如果你想了解宅女们的深闺,那这本揭秘日本宅女闺房的写真集一定能满足你的所有好奇心。<br/>  
16293829	床上一分钟,床下十年功	  <!--$image=&quot;http://00f3c1b4.sohunewsclientpic.imgcdn.sohucs.com/img8/wb/smccloud/fetch/2014/02/17/87533908746721310.gif&quot;--><br/>  床上一分钟,床下十年功
16346618	【郑州·乐活】本周食材	<p style=&quot;margin-top:10.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.5pt;margin-left:<br/>0cm;line-height:16.8pt&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>如果说有什么需要感恩上帝的话,我首先想感谢祂老人家给了我一张百无禁忌的嘴。每次听到有人跟老板交待:不要放##,我总忍不住给他投去一个同情的眼神,人生短短几十年,多一个忌口就少一份享受。不吃香菇的体会不到那种丰满的咬合感,不吃香菜的感受不到骨白热汤激发出的碧绿清香,不吃韭菜的无法明白一道简单的山韭菜炒蛋是怎样的清新脱俗&hellip;&hellip;至于不吃羊肉的朋友,唉,人生至此,天可怜见,想吃点啥就吃点啥吧。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787741411.jpg&quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>倒春寒的二三月,羊肉是最合适不过的食材,不但美味,而且能量满满。&ldquo;东门彘肉更奇绝,肥美不减胡羊酥&rdquo; 是陆游盛赞羊肉酥软浓香的诗句。羊肉与猪肉、牛肉相比,肉质更细嫩,脂肪和胆固醇含量也更少,最适合冬季炖煮,有进补和防寒的双重佳效。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787741594.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉的营养价值很高,《本草纲目》记载&ldquo;羊肉能暖中补虚,补中益气,开胃健身,养胆明目&rdquo;。现代营养学发现,羊肉含有丰富的蛋白质,其含量较猪肉牛肉高出不少,除此,钙、铁、维生素C等微量元素的含量都大为突出。羊肉性温,冬季常吃羊肉,不仅可以增加人体热量,御寒冷,而且还能增加消化酶,保护胃壁帮助消化。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787741753.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>购买羊肉时要求外观完整,瘦肉色泽红润,脂肪为白色或奶油色,表面湿润且富有弹性。如果羊肉色暗淡,脂肪缺乏光泽,用手压后凹陷复原慢,且不能完全恢复到原状,则表明羊肉已经不新鲜。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787741953.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉料理小贴士:不吃羊肉的人大多是因为不喜欢羊肉的膻味,其实有膻味的多为山羊肉,绵羊肉是不膻的;另外,提前用洋葱、料酒、甘草等腌制,或者炒制时加入葱、姜、孜然等佐料一起烹调,也能够去掉膻气又可保持羊肉风味。夏秋季节气候燥热,最好少吃羊肉。&nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787742133.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>【灰太狼的祖传食谱】</strong><br /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&nbsp;&bull;</span><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&nbsp;羊肉炖白萝卜</strong><br /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉搭配萝卜是无可替代的官方推荐配置,就如同猪肉与粉条、鱼肉与豆腐。&nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787742304.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>用料:</strong><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉、白萝卜、枸杞、葱姜、白酒、胡椒粉、盐</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>做法:</strong><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>1.羊肉切块,白萝卜去皮切块,姜切片;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>2.锅中放入清水,羊肉凉水下锅,待水烧开,待血沫膻味除净,捞出冲净待用;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>3.锅中坐开水,放入焯净的羊肉块,葱、姜,大火烧开烹入白酒,改中火煨1小时;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>4.打开锅盖放入焯过水的白萝卜,改大火煮30分钟,加盐、胡椒粉调味;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>5.看到白萝卜变软透明即可出锅,放入提前烧热的石锅中撒枸杞、香菜叶保温食用。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&bull;&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>回锅羊肉</strong><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>经典回锅肉的羊肉版本,还是一样的配方,还是原来的味道&hellip;&hellip;可能更骚一点。</strong><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787742470.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>用料:</strong><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉、葱姜、豆瓣酱、蒜苗、料酒、花椒、洋葱&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>做法:&nbsp;</strong><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>1.将羊肉凉水下锅,加料酒、姜片、花椒粒和洋葱煮开,捞出血沫;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>2.至七八成熟时捞出,切片备用;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>3.下油,将豆瓣酱炒香后放干辣椒和羊肉,加少许盐;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>4.蒜苗切段下锅,稍事翻炒就起锅,羊肉咸鲜微辣,蒜香浓郁。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>&bull;&nbsp;</span><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>意大利羊肉浓汤</strong><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉是民族的,羊肉是世界的!郑州有无数家#记羊汤,可惜都不太适合约会,学会这道洋气的意式羊肉浓汤,亲手炮制招待女神,绝对靠谱。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><img alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392787742648.jpg&quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>用料:</strong><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>羊肉、胡萝卜、洋葱、土豆、西芹、番茄酱、黄油&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>做法: &nbsp;</strong><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>1.把所有的材料切成小块;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>2.锅里加一小块黄油,把羊肉加进去炒到变色,加点黑胡椒粉,加水炖煮;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>3.大火烧开后十五分钟,把所有的蔬菜都扔进锅里,然后浇上番茄酱小火咕咚;</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>4.盖上锅盖耐心等待约四十分钟,羊肉熟了就好;蔬菜炖烂了不要紧,浓汤嘛。</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>注:部分菜谱来自下厨房app</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>(文字/吕有品&nbsp; 图片来自于网络)</span><br style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot; /><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, verdana; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 23px; &quot;>版权所有,如欲转载,需获本编辑部同意。</span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top:10.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.5pt;margin-left:<br/>0cm;line-height:16.8pt&quot;><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; &quot;>&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; &quot;><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=&quot;margin-top:10.5pt;margin-right:0cm;m