ing-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>接下来的微博文案,就可以肆意造句了:</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>家长注意:今晚,别让孩子单独出门吃元宵。</span></p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>&ldquo;妈妈,今晚我去同学家吃汤圆哦。&rdquo;</span></p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-hei