b(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>那么,先给大象想一个slogan吧。</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>大象,大象,你的鼻子怎么这么长&hellip;&hellip;你当这是动画片么?虽然大象是个以年轻群体为主要对象的品牌,但这个也太低龄了。</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>要来一发有逼格但是又不失青春、有趣味的slogan,怎么撸?</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>大象的网站首页上的第一个卖点就是:极限超薄工艺。再看安全套这个产品本身的特性,就是要在安全的基础上尽量的薄,薄到戴跟不戴一样的境界,你就赢了。</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>这时,老子忽然跳了出来说:大象无形。</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>整个广告创意就出来了,广告图如下:</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><img style=&quot;border-right-width: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: auto !important; border-left-width: 0px&quot; src=&quot;http://cache.k.sohu.com/img8/wb/2014/02/19/1392800789015.jpg&quot; data-pinit=&quot;registered&quot; data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/5yRw1rPKEdORD4RiaL73peHCnCo11fyt9iak0xq0bc142DzMUbdpNTtmzFyeR9ZwEO1juPibS1j26jXtbNLicsc9Sw/0&quot; /></p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>(请忽略我渣一般的PS技术)</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wr