hite-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>大音希呻</span>(注意是呻吟的呻,不是声音的声,主要诉求是极致的体验)</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>在情人节这样特殊的日子里,我们可以来几个有趣的切合节日的系列文案:</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>情人节,要故事不要事故</span>(安全性)</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>情人节,要有劲不要蛮劲</span>(包装设计也是大象的一个特点,撕开包装很容易,把力量专注在OOXX上就好了)</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;><span style=&quot;color: rgb(0,176,240)&quot;>情人节,要情趣不要恶趣</span>(大象会赠送很多小玩意,增加OOXX的情趣)</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/2em 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(62,62,62); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0p